OL,6,FITV News can reveal that driving test
OL,7,Fofficials will face tough questions in
OL,8,FParliament over issues caused by long
OL,9,Fwaiting lists for driving tests,
OL,10,FConsumer Editor Chris Choi reports
OL,12,FUnofficial sellers of driving test
OL,13,Fslots in the UK are charging around
OL,14,Ffour times the official rate, ITV News
OL,15,Fhas found.
