OL,3,CLearner drivers paying up to #242 as
OL,4,Ctouts cash-in on driving license delays
OL,6,FOfficial figures show learners are
OL,7,Ftypically waiting more than five
OL,8,Fmonths to take their tests in some
OL,9,Fparts of the UK. Meanwhile, the test
OL,10,Ftouts are cashing in on the
OL,11,Fdesperation - and we've learned that
OL,12,FMPs are soon to question officials on
OL,13,Fwhat can be done about it.
OL,15,FFor thousands of learner drivers,
OL,16,Fgetting a test slot has become the
OL,17,Fmost difficult maneuver. Their
OL,18,Fstruggle has opened up an unofficial
OL,19,Fmarket of driving test touts, charging
OL,20,Ffar more than the official #62 fee.
