OL,3,CLearner drivers paying up to #242 as
OL,4,Ctouts cash-in on driving license delays
OL,6,FWe spoke to new driver, 19-year-old
OL,7,FTasha Grant, who told us: "Everyone my
OL,8,Fage...everyone's trying to find a
OL,9,Ftest, so I paid double the #60... I
OL,10,Fpaid #150".
OL,12,FThe latest official figures show the
OL,13,Fshortest test wait time is in Wales at
OL,14,Fjust over three months, or 12.8 weeks.
OL,15,FScotland is now around four months, or
OL,16,F15.6 weeks.
OL,18,FEngland has the longest waits clocking
OL,19,Fup from 14.5 two years ago to more
OL,20,Fthan 20.5 weeks today - that is more
OL,21,Fthan a five-month wait.
