OL,3,CLearner drivers paying up to #242 as
OL,4,Ctouts cash-in on driving license delays
OL,6,FITV News found people re-selling test
OL,7,Fslots across social media and on
OL,8,Findividual websites, with prices
OL,9,Franging from around #125 up to #242.
OL,11,FA theory test usually costs #23 for
OL,12,Fcars, while a driving test costs #62,
OL,13,Faccording to a government website.
OL,15,FIt's all brought dismay in driving
OL,16,Fschools across the UK as officials
OL,17,Ffail to bring down test waiting lists.
