OL,6,FDriving instructor Duygu Ozcan told
OL,7,Fus: "I think it's a shambles, it's not
OL,8,Ffair that people have to pay extra to
OL,9,Fa third party that isn't even
OL,10,Frecognised and some people are getting
OL,11,Fscammed".
OL,13,FRuth Cadbury MP, who heads the
OL,14,Fparliamentary Transport Committee,
OL,15,Fsays driving test officials face tough
OL,16,Fquestions, saying: "This should not be
OL,17,Fa private sector profiteering racket.
OL,18,FThis should be what's really important
OL,19,Fto people.
